NAME
<style color=#00ffffff size=1>.</style>            runas - run command as another user

SYNOPSIS
<style color=#00ffffff size=1>.</style>            runas user cmd \[ arg... \]

DESCRIPTION
<style color=#00ffffff size=1>.</style>            Runas writes user to /dev/user and invokes cmd with the
<style color=#00ffffff size=1>.</style>            given arguments. The command is only invoked if setting of
<style color=#00ffffff size=1>.</style>            the user name succeeds.

SOURCE
<style color=#00ffffff size=1>.</style>            /appl/cmd/runas.b

SEE ALSO
<style color=#00ffffff size=1>.</style>            <action name=cons(3)>cons(3)</action>,

<style color=#00ffffff size=1>.</style>                                Inferno Manual
